    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Ambrose King Ministries is dedicated to spreading the message of the Kingdom, teaching the Word of God with clarity, and empowering believers to live victorious lives in Christ.</p>
    <p>Founded by <strong>Pastor Ambrose King Snr</strong>, the ministry combines preaching, teaching, outreach, and community service to impact lives locally and globally.</p>
    <p>We demonstrate the love of Christ through practical service — supporting the homeless and orphans, mentoring believers, and equipping men and women to live with Kingdom authority.</p>
